text: Helen Elizabeth "Tess" Daly (born 29 March 1969) is an English model, novelist and television presenter. She is best known for co-presenting the BBC One celebrity dancing show Strictly Come Dancing since 2004. Daly was born in Stockport, Cheshire. In 2003 she married Vernon Kay.
